    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>331520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_096&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオス……本当にあなたは
変わってしまったんだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos...So it really is true.
You truly have changed...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>331816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_099&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえは、私のことなど
何も知っていない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You know nothing concerning me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>331816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_100&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私にあるのは後悔と復讐、
それのみだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The only thing left inside me
is regret and apprehension. </EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL checkApprehenshion</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>331940</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_101&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオス、どうして……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos...why?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>331940</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_102&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>後悔……復讐……
何のための……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Regret...Apprehension...But for what reason?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check Apprehenshion</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_103&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ここにいたダオスは
別の時空から飛んできた
ダオスだったのか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That Dhaos just now...
Could he have travelled
here from a different time?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_104&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;……
気がすんだか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey &lt;Rody&gt;...everything ok?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332244</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_105&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ごめん……
みんなにはいろいろ、
迷惑かけちゃったね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm so sorry...I've been putting everyone
in danger for my own selfish reasons
this whole time...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_106&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私は幼い時、ダオスと、
世界樹の前で出会った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I met Dhaos when I was really small,
in front of the Mana Tree.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_107&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーン……
自分の故郷に『大いなる実り』を
持ち帰るためにそこへ来てた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He told me of Derris Kharlan...
How he needed a Mana Seed
to return to his home planet...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_108&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの頃、優しくて、
思慮深いヤツだったよ、
あいつは</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At that time, he was so very kind
to me. He used to be a very
thoughtful and gentle man.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_109&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスが……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Our Dhaos?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_110&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう。だから、そんな彼が、
人類に戦争を仕掛けた張本人
だなんてとても思えなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, the same. That's why when I heard he
was spearheading a war against humanity, I
couldn't bring myself to believe it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_111&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、確かめたかった。
ダオスがあのダオスなのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's the reason I had to be sure
if that Dhaos was my Dhaos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_112&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだとしたら、
止めなきゃって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And if that was the case...
promised myself I'd stop him
with my own two hands.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_113&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、怖くて聞けなかった……
何も、ちゃんと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I never imagined it would
be so scary. It was all true...
everything they said...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>332932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_114&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私ってダメなヤツ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guess I never was cut
out for the job, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_115&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……
&lt;Rody&gt;さん、
ダオスのこと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see...Miss &lt;Rody&gt; and Dhaos...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333116</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_116&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ん……あれ……
何があった、の……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Uh...wh-what just...happened...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_117&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>気がついたか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you up?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333268</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_118&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………？
ねぇ、これ、
何かな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...? Hey, what's this thingamajig?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333360</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_119&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これは……！
魔科学兵器のかけらだ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't believe it...! It's the fragment
of a Magitech weapon! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333424</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_120&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだって？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What did you say?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_121&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ&lt;White&gt;で『シグルド』が
使ってたものじゃないかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>These seem to be leftovers from
Sigurd's attack on &lt;Red&gt;Valhalla&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_122&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>爆発すると自動的に
詠唱を続けて、
魔法を継続させる兵器だよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's a weapon that destroys the nearby landscape
by continuously casting spells automatically, quickly
depleting the surrounding Mana.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_123&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これだよ！
『虹輪』の原因！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's it! This is the source of the Prism Ring!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_124&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしが魔術を使ったはずみに
爆発して……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You mean it wasn't the explosion
caused by my magic...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>333884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_125&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ……&lt;Mel&gt;の
せいじゃねーよな、
これって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This means...it never was
&lt;Mel&gt;'s fault to begin with!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_126&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>せいじゃないってことはないよ。
爆発させた原因はわたしだもん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I may not have caused it,
but the explosion definitely
set the machine off.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_127&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……でも、よかった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yet...I'm so relieved...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_128&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたし、魔術使うたび怖かった。
また暴走させちゃうんじゃ
ないかって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All this time... I've been so very
scared of my magic causing a
disaster again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_129&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん……よかったよ、
本当に……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...it's a huge relief...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_130&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ま、これで
一件落着ってことかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, that means everything
is settled now, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334404</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_131&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりのことも見届けられたし、
自分たちの時代に戻ろうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Since we've made sure you guys
could finish your job, it's about
time we returned to our own eras.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_132&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>指輪も
いい感じになってるし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Looks like my ring is
ready to rock, too!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_133&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私がみんなを元の時代に
送ったげるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How about I send you
back to your own times?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334632</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_134&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;はどうすんだ。
またダオスを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, what now, &lt;Rody&gt;?
I mean, Dhaos is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_135&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>できればそうしたいけど、
どこ行ったかわかんないし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I could try to track him down,
but I don't have the slightest
idea where he went.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_136&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この指輪の気まぐれに
付き合ってみてもいいかなって。
風の向くままにさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've grown a bit tired of the whims of
this ring, to be honest. So I might try
to track him down with normal means.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_137&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あっ……来た……
ほら、みんな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Speaking of which...
It's time, everyone!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>334996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_138&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、
&lt;Dio&gt;、&lt;Mel&gt;、がんばって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In that case...&lt;Dio&gt;, &lt;Mel&gt;,
always do your best!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_139&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;、元気でな。
寂しくて、泣くなよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's been nice &lt;Arche&gt;... If you
get sad...don't cry, kay?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335180</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_140&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>泣くかっ！
このスカポンタン！
空気読め！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I won't cry you insensitive jerk!
Way to ruin the mood.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_141&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おふたりに会えて、
友達ができたみたいで
楽しかったです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I am glad we met. It has
been a really fun experience.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_142&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとうございます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you, from the
bottom of my heart.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_143&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>みたい、と違うだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's way too formal, yknow!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>46</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_144&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>友達だもんね、
わたしたち</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We're friends from now on!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>47</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_145&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……はい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>48</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_146&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>終わったね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's all over...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>49</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_147&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、終わった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes...it really is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>50</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_148&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ってまだ
終わってねーだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>--Wait, the hell it's over!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>50</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_149&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wha?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>52</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_150&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だってノルンに言われた
『なりきり士』の仕事
オレら、なんもしてねーぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Have you forgotten? We've got
work as Roleplayers to do!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>53</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>335996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_151&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……そうだっけ……
そうだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh...yeah I forgot...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>54</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_152&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>自分たちで事件起こして
自分たちで解決しただけだもんね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think, after all you've been through,
that was easy to forget.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>55</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_153&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし！　行くぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! Let's go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>56</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336272</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_154&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どーせ、またどこ行くか、
わかってないんでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Where to? You have
no idea, do you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>57</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_155&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかんねーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nope.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>58</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_156&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも……
わかんねーから
おもしれーんじゃん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...not knowing is the
most fun, isn't it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>58</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_157&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、&lt;Dio&gt;……
まったく、もう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, &lt;Dio&gt;! And there he goes...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>60</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_158&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おもしろい、かな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fun...huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>61</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_159&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……うん、そうかも！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>61</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336740</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_160&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、&lt;Mel&gt;まで……！！
まったく……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not &lt;Mel&gt; too! Really...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>63</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>336740</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_240_010_161&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あー待ってよ！
置いてかないで～！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>H-Hey, wait! Don't leave me here!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>63</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
